menu "Gamepad Gateway"

    config VERBOSE_HID_DEBUG
        bool "Verbose HID debug instrumentation"
        default n
        help
            Enables targeted instrumentation used to debug HID report decoding
            and multi-device merge behavior (e.g., the rudder axis issue).

            When enabled, the firmware will:
              - Dump a descriptor snapshot once per device connect
              - Track per-device report cadence and last report metadata
              - Print per-device decoded state before merging
              - Print per-axis merge "winner" device and collisions

            Keep this OFF for release builds to reduce log noise and overhead.

endmenu
